                </div>

                <p>DropLaa is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). This page outlines how we comply with GDPR requirements and what rights you have regarding your personal data.</p>

                <div class="compliance-checklist">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>Our GDPR Compliance Measures</h3>
